track_notes: Use track near the summit to find the trail to the summit.
Recognizable trails, to within 100yds of summit, although some of them are not on the maps.
track_title: Route Up Greenbrier Knob, on trails.

track_notes: Treated this more like a trail run. Too many ticks. If I ever come back Ill be slathered in DEET and Permethrin.
